<div class=3D"bodyHeader">Semaphore flags</div>
<div class=3D"bodySection"><p>
Semaphore flags is the system for conveying information at a distance by me=
ans of visual signals with hand-held flags, rods, disks, paddles or occasio=
nally bare hands. Information is encoded by the position of the flags; it i=
s read when the flag is in a fixed position. Semaphores were adopted and wi=
dely used in the maritime world in the 19th century.
</p></div>
